---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Resume" sideBarActiveItemID="cv">

  <!-- Header + Download button -->
  <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-8 flex-wrap gap-4">
    <div>
      <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Resume</div>
    </div>
    <a
      href="/JhamesAndrewMacabata_Resume.pdf"
      download
      class="btn btn-neutral btn-sm gap-2"
    >
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 16.5v2.25A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0021 18.75V16.5M16.5 12L12 16.5m0 0L7.5 12m4.5 4.5V3" />
      </svg>
      Download PDF
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class="divider my-2"></div>

  <!-- Summary -->
  <div class="mb-6">
    <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 mb-4">Summary</div>
    <p class="text-sm opacity-75 leading-relaxed">
      CS graduate with ~1 year of professional experience building and shipping full-stack web
      applications, REST APIs, containerized backend services, data pipelines, and ML models.
      Proven across the full development lifecycle — from system design to CI/CD and production
      deployment. All major projects are live and deployed.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="divider my-2"></div>

  <!-- Work Experience -->
  <div class="mb-6">
    <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 mb-4">Work Experience</div>

    <div class="mb-2">
      <div class="flex justify-between items-start flex-wrap gap-1 mb-2">
        <div>
          <div class="font-bold">Software Developer Intern / Team Lead</div>
          <div class="text-sm opacity-60">8Con Academy</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-sm opacity-50">May 2025 – Present</div>
      </div>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm opacity-75 space-y-1 ml-1">
        <li>Developed and maintained web-based systems and automation tools supporting business operations.</li>
        <li>Built automated lead capture pipeline — website form submissions are routed and logged to a CRM in real time.</li>
        <li>Led frontend and backend development tasks across multiple web projects.</li>
        <li>Produced technical documentation including system flowcharts, code comments, and deployment procedures.</li>
        <li>Collaborated with team members and stakeholders to deliver scalable solutions.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="divider my-2"></div>

  <!-- Projects -->
  <div class="mb-6">
    <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 mb-4">Projects</div>

    <div class="space-y-5">

      <div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start flex-wrap gap-1">
          <div>
            <div class="font-bold">8Con Edge — Thesis Project</div>
            <div class="text-xs opacity-55 italic">Lead Developer · React 19 · Express 5 · Flask · MySQL · Docker</div>
          </div>
          <a href="https://8conedge.com" target="_blank" class="text-xs link link-hover opacity-50">8conedge.com</a>
        </div>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm opacity-75 space-y-1 ml-1 mt-1">
          <li>Full-stack forex trading decision support system used by 20–50 students.</li>
          <li>ML-powered pair-ranking replaced a fully manual process — reduced currency analysis time from hours to minutes, surfacing strength/weakness scores to aid trade bias decisions.</li>
          <li>Features role-based and tier-based access control. Deployed to production.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start flex-wrap gap-1">
          <div>
            <div class="font-bold">JobTrail</div>
            <div class="text-xs opacity-55 italic">Developer · FastAPI · PostgreSQL · HTMX · Tailwind · Supabase Auth · GitHub Actions</div>
          </div>
          <a href="https://jobtrail-0gza.onrender.com" target="_blank" class="text-xs link link-hover opacity-50">jobtrail-0gza.onrender.com</a>
        </div>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm opacity-75 space-y-1 ml-1 mt-1">
          <li>Job application tracker with magic-link auth, inline editing, status filtering, and live dashboard.</li>
          <li>Includes 10 pytest tests covering CRUD, auth guards, and user isolation. Full CI/CD pipeline on every push.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start flex-wrap gap-1">
          <div>
            <div class="font-bold">MiniLink</div>
            <div class="text-xs opacity-55 italic">Developer · FastAPI · PostgreSQL · Redis · Docker · Railway · GitHub Actions</div>
          </div>
          <a href="https://minilink-production.up.railway.app" target="_blank" class="text-xs link link-hover opacity-50">minilink-production.up.railway.app</a>
        </div>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm opacity-75 space-y-1 ml-1 mt-1">
          <li>Self-hosted URL shortener with redirect analytics. Multi-stage Docker build (~150MB image), Redis read-through cache with 24h TTL.</li>
          <li>Full CI/CD pipeline — lint → test → build → push to GHCR → Railway autodeploy.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start flex-wrap gap-1">
          <div>
            <div class="font-bold">CryptoPulse</div>
            <div class="text-xs opacity-55 italic">Developer · Python · DuckDB · dbt · Streamlit · GitHub Actions · Parquet</div>
          </div>
          <a href="https://cryptopulse.streamlit.app" target="_blank" class="text-xs link link-hover opacity-50">cryptopulse.streamlit.app</a>
        </div>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm opacity-75 space-y-1 ml-1 mt-1">
          <li>Automated ETL pipeline running every 6 hours via GitHub Actions cron — fetches top-100 crypto market data, writes Parquet snapshots, loads into DuckDB, runs dbt transformations, serves a live Streamlit dashboard.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start flex-wrap gap-1">
          <div>
            <div class="font-bold">StaySure — Hotel Cancellation Predictor</div>
            <div class="text-xs opacity-55 italic">Developer · Python · scikit-learn · XGBoost · SHAP · Gradio</div>
          </div>
          <a href="https://huggingface.co/spaces/neuralxjam/staysure" target="_blank" class="text-xs link link-hover opacity-50">huggingface.co/spaces/neuralxjam/staysure</a>
        </div>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm opacity-75 space-y-1 ml-1 mt-1">
          <li>Trained on 119,390 hotel bookings. Best model: Random Forest — F1=0.85, AUC=0.958, Accuracy=89%.</li>
          <li>Compared 3 baselines (LR, XGBoost, RF). Added SHAP explainability layer. Deployed on Hugging Face Spaces.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start flex-wrap gap-1">
          <div>
            <div class="font-bold">8Con Academy Website — Internship Project</div>
            <div class="text-xs opacity-55 italic">Team Lead Developer · JavaScript · HTML5 · CSS3 · SMTP</div>
          </div>
          <a href="https://8conacademy.com" target="_blank" class="text-xs link link-hover opacity-50">8conacademy.com</a>
        </div>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm opacity-75 space-y-1 ml-1 mt-1">
          <li>Full-stack web platform with SMTP-based transactional email, form validation, and database-connected lead capture workflows.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start flex-wrap gap-1">
          <div>
            <div class="font-bold">J.Kloting Website + Dashboard — Client Project</div>
            <div class="text-xs opacity-55 italic">Developer · HTML5 · CSS3 · JavaScript · AJAX · Next.js · TypeScript · Supabase</div>
          </div>
          <a href="https://jkloting.store" target="_blank" class="text-xs link link-hover opacity-50">jkloting.store</a>
        </div>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm opacity-75 space-y-1 ml-1 mt-1">
          <li>Client-facing e-commerce site with dynamic form handling and a separate admin dashboard built in Next.js with Supabase.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start flex-wrap gap-1">
          <div>
            <div class="font-bold">PCCI Membership Platform — Client Project</div>
            <div class="text-xs opacity-55 italic">Developer · Laravel 12 · PostgreSQL · Sanctum · Tailwind</div>
          </div>
          <a href="https://pcci-frontend-staging.onrender.com" target="_blank" class="text-xs link link-hover opacity-50">pcci-frontend-staging.onrender.com (staging)</a>
        </div>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm opacity-75 space-y-1 ml-1 mt-1">
          <li>Membership management system for a Philippine chamber of commerce — role-based dues tracking, multi-channel payments, and automated notifications. Currently in development.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start flex-wrap gap-1">
          <div>
            <div class="font-bold">Roos & Lyka Wedding RSVP — Event Site</div>
            <div class="text-xs opacity-55 italic">Developer · HTML5 · CSS3 · JavaScript</div>
          </div>
          <a href="https://excroosivelymeantforlyka.netlify.app" target="_blank" class="text-xs link link-hover opacity-50">excroosivelymeantforlyka.netlify.app</a>
        </div>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm opacity-75 space-y-1 ml-1 mt-1">
          <li>Custom wedding RSVP page for a live event. Statically deployed on Netlify.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="divider my-2"></div>

  <!-- Education -->
  <div class="mb-10">
    <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 mb-4">Education</div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start flex-wrap gap-1">
          <div>
            <div class="font-bold">Bachelor of Science in Computer Science</div>
            <div class="text-sm opacity-60">Pambayang Dalubhasaan ng Marilao</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-sm opacity-50">August 2022 – May 2026</div>
        </div>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm opacity-75 space-y-1 ml-1 mt-1">
          <li>2026 Computer Science Best Thesis Award</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start flex-wrap gap-1">
          <div>
            <div class="font-bold">BS Electrical Engineering (transferred to CS)</div>
            <div class="text-sm opacity-60">Polytechnic University of the Philippines, Sta. Mesa</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-sm opacity-50">Aug 2020 – Feb 2022</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>
